        "last_activity_date": 1422019585,
        "creation_date": 1422019585,
        "body": "<p>If you are using https, you have to add following to your axis2.xml file<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>&lt;transportReceiver name=\"https\"\n                   class=\"org.apache.axis2.transport.http.AxisServletListener\"&gt;\n    &lt;parameter name=\"port\"&gt;8443&lt;/parameter&gt;\n&lt;/transportReceiver&gt;\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>(<a href=\"http://dulanja.blogspot.de/2012/12/why-tomcat-gives-internal-server-error.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">full article<\/a>)<\/p>\n\n<p>This enables https listeren for axis2. It is not enabled by default (unlike http access) .<\/p>\n\n<p>the axis2.xml file can be found here:<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>$CATALINA_HOME/webapps/axis2/WEB-INF/conf/axis2.xml\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
